# {{ project_name }}

A minimalist Machine Learning Pipeline with a "Cold Start" capability.

## Why this Architecture?
This pipeline is designed for immediate testing. By relying on synthetic data generation (`make_classification`), you can verify that your Gradient Forest model and evaluation metrics work *before* you spend hours cleaning a real dataset.

## Philosophy
**{{ philosophy|capitalize }}**

{% if philosophy == 'speed' %}
